  "description": "A showdown in [poker](../index.md) is the stage at the end of a [hand](./hand.md) where the remaining players reveal their cards to determine who wins the [pot](./pot.md) [@britannica2026poker]. A hand reaches showdown only if betting does not end it earlier.",
